description:
Edit the file app/config/agent-settings.json. Find the "builder" entry and replace its entire configuration with this:

```json
"builder": {
  "adapter": "deepseek",
  "model": "deepseek-chat",
  "temperature": 0.2,
  "max_tokens": 8096,
  "fallbacks": [
    {
      "adapter": "deepseek",
      "model": "deepseek-reasoner"
    },
    {
      "adapter": "anthropic",
      "model": "claude-sonnet-4-6"
    },
    {
      "adapter": "openai",
      "model": "gpt-4o-mini"
    }
  ]
}
```

Do NOT modify any other agent's config. Validate the JSON is valid after editing. Apply the change directly — no approval needed, this has already been approved.

